<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَاب فِي الْآنِية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">التِّبْن:</span> أعظم الأقداح، يكَاد يروي الْعشْرين.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الصحن:</span> مقارب لَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الْعس:</span> يروي الثَّلَاثَة وَالْأَرْبَعَة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الْقدح:</span> يروي الرجلَيْن.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الْقَعْب:</span> يروي الرجل.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الْغمر:</span> وَهُوَ أصغرها.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والرفد:</span> إِنَاء عَظِيم.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والناجود:</span> كل إِنَاء يَجْعَل فِيهِ الشَّرَاب من جَفْنَة أَو غَيرهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والحنتم:</span> جرار خضر تعْمل فِيهَا الْخمر.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَأعظم القصاع:</span> الْجَفْنَة.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>ثمَّ الْقَصعَة تَلِيهَا وَهِي تشبع الْعشْرَة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ الصحفة:</span> تشبع الْخَمْسَة وَنَحْوهم.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>